OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells with the odd evening shower,
OL,7,Fthese mostly in the north. Staying
OL,8,Fmainly dry overnight but becoming
OL,9,Fcloudy with some patchy light rain in
OL,10,Fthe southwest later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with patchy
OL,13,Flight rain in west during the morning.
OL,14,FThe rain will spread east and become
OL,15,Fheavier near the west coast in
OL,16,Fafternoon. North Highland staying
OL,17,Fmainly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
